          <li>Frequently Asked Questions</li>
        </ul>
        <p><a href="../sponsors/sponsors/dan_info_for_supporters.php">CLICK HERE</a> to view the page.        </p>
        <h2>Is Your Business Listed on the DAN AP website?</h2>
        <p>Is your business currently being promoted on the DAN AP website? Many Supporters have taken advantage of this opportunity but still many haven&rsquo;t. </p>
        <p>The DAN Asia-Pacific website offers a fantastic opportunity to promote your business. Traffic visiting the DAN AP website is made up 100% of divers, i.e. YOUR TARGET MARKET! If you are not listed on the DAN AP website you are missing out on a great &ldquo;Free&rdquo; opportunity.</p>
